---
import Layout from "../layouts/BlogPost.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="we are a team of developers who are passionate about building web applications"
  pubDate={new Date("February 04 2025")}
  heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
  <div class="about-content">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Who We Are</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Capaxe Labs is a Silicon Valley-based team of passionate Shopify experts and web developers dedicated to empowering e-commerce businesses.
      Founded on the principles of technical excellence and client-focused solutions, we've established ourselves as trusted partners for businesses
      looking to thrive in the digital marketplace.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Our mission is to deliver cutting-edge Shopify solutions that drive e-commerce success. We believe in creating digital experiences that not only
      look beautiful but also perform exceptionally well, helping our clients achieve their business goals and exceed customer expectations.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Expertise</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Shopify Development</h3>
        <p>
          From custom theme development to complex store setups, we specialize in creating tailored Shopify experiences that convert visitors into
          customers.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Custom App Development</h3>
        <p>We build bespoke applications that extend Shopify's functionality, solving unique business challenges and streamlining operations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">E-commerce Solutions</h3>
        <p>
          Our comprehensive e-commerce solutions include everything from store setup and migration to performance optimization and ongoing
          maintenance.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Web Development</h3>
        <p>We create modern, responsive websites using cutting-edge technologies that provide exceptional user experiences across all devices.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Choose Us</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Technical Excellence:</strong> Our team stays at the forefront of e-commerce technology to deliver innovative solutions.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Client-Focused Approach:</strong> We listen carefully to your needs and tailor our services to meet your specific business goals.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Proven Track Record:</strong> Our portfolio showcases successful projects across various industries, demonstrating our versatility and
        expertise.
      </li>
      <li class="mb-3">
        <strong>Ongoing Support:</strong> We offer flexible retainer plans to provide continuous improvements and support for long-term success.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Team</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Behind Capaxe Labs is a diverse team of developers, designers, and e-commerce strategists who bring a wealth of experience and creativity to
      every project. We're united by our passion for building exceptional digital experiences and our commitment to helping businesses succeed online.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to transform your e-commerce business?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        Whether you're looking to launch a new Shopify store, enhance your existing one, or need ongoing development support, we're here to help.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >Get in Touch</a
      >
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
